  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/c29732e8909f65cb369703379954294c.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/c29732e8909f65cb369703379954294c.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/c29732e8909f65cb369703379954294c.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be able to change the game mode to online cooperation, even if you start in single player mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own farm and produce food. Use your cooking pot and discover different types of meals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the necessary resources to build your base, fix damaged items and complete quests. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/faf14dcf697976e5de4026f1a4a64843.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/faf14dcf697976e5de4026f1a4a64843.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/faf14dcf697976e5de4026f1a4a64843.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and improve your bases! Produce and store electrical energy. Be prepared for enemy raids! Each biome allows you to build various unique items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/a91c0ab9a475f93b18504822df17ed93.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/a91c0ab9a475f93b18504822df17ed93.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/a91c0ab9a475f93b18504822df17ed93.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and improve your equipment. A good weapon and armor will help you survive, but when your opponent is much stronger than you - better run away!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/c29732e8909f65cb369703379954294c.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/c29732e8909f65cb369703379954294c.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/c29732e8909f65cb369703379954294c.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be able to change the game mode to online cooperation, even if you start in single player mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.webm?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.mp4?t=1770728819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own farm and produce food. Use your cooking pot and discover different types of meals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323900/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.poster.avif?t=1770728819\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/